inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
MicrosoftHealthcareApisAuditLogs 
| where ResultType == "Failed" 
| summarize Requests = count() by bin(TimeGenerated, 1h)

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
union isfuzzy=true
    availabilityResults,
    requests,
    exceptions,
    pageViews,
    traces,
    customEvents,
    dependencies
| order by timestamp desc
| take 100
| summarize Logs = count() by itemType

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
union isfuzzy=true
    availabilityResults,

    dependencies
| order by timestamp desc
